==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: cuckoo bee
<hw>cuckoo bee</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <def>a bee,
parasitic in the larval stage in the nests of other bees, feeding either
upon their food or larvae. They belong to the genera <gen>Nomada</gen>,
<gen>Melecta</gen>, <gen>Epeolus</gen>, and others.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>cuckoo-bumblebee</ent>⟦br⟧
